    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='221:248'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-1a' );" name="016-1a" class="pb">[016-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='248:261'>禮記要義卷第十七　少儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='261:273'>一適有䘮者曰比曰聽事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='273:293'>適有䘮者曰比童子曰聽事注云適之也曰某</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='293:313'>願比於將命者比猶比方俱給事曰某願聽事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='313:333'>於將命者童子未成人不敢當相見之禮正義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='333:353'>曰此謂徃適者䘮家也比比方也䘮不主相見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='353:373'>凡徃者皆是助事故云比謂比方其年力以給</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='373:393'>䘮事也若五十從反哭四十待盈坎皆是比方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='393:413'>其事故鄭云比謂比方俱給事故辭云願比於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='413:440'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-1b' );" name="016-1b" class="pb">[016-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='440:446'>將命者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='446:470'>　二主人無親受<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0608' title='KR0608' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0608.png'/>非尸柩之事不親</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='470:497'><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0608' title='KR0608' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0608.png'/>者旣致命坐委之擯者舉之主人無親受也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='497:517'>注云䘮者非尸柩之事不親也舉之舉以東正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='517:537'>義曰吉時若人饋物主人皆自拜受之若有䘮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='537:564'>主於哀戚凡有四方使者以物<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0608' title='KR0608' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0608.png'/>己悉不得拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='564:584'>受故使擯者受舉之而巳知舉以東者雜記云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='584:604'>含者入升堂致命坐委于殯東南宰夫朝服即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='604:624'>䘮屨升自西階西面坐取璧降自西階以東後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='624:651'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-2a' );" name="016-2a" class="pb">[016-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='651:678'>禭者<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0608' title='KR0608' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0608.png'/>者並然而升堂致命是告殯之辭也若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='678:705'><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0608' title='KR0608' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0608.png'/>生人則致命擯者不告殯而不升堂然車馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='705:723'>不舉以東而鄭云舉以東者謂幣之屬也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='723:737'>　三不疑不度不願不訾四事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='737:757'>不疑在躬者旣問主人之道藝則巳亦當習學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='757:777'>明了不得使疑事在其躬而爲賔爲主皆然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='777:797'>　不度民械者謂爲客至主人之家不得度民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='797:817'>家所有器械使已亦有也　不願於大家者大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='817:837'>家謂冨貴廣大之家謂大夫之家也謂士徃於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='837:864'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-2b' );" name="016-2b" class="pb">[016-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='864:884'>卿大夫之見彼冨大不可願斆之也非分而願</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='884:904'>必有亂心也　不訾重器者訾思也重器寳珍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='904:924'>之物主謂客至主人之家見有珍物重器不可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='924:944'>思玩之若思玩之則憎疾已貧賤生淫亂濫惡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='944:950'>也<span class='krp-note'>䟽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='950:966'>　四婦人以肅拜爲正凶事乃手拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='966:986'>婦人吉事雖有君賜肅拜爲尸坐則不手拜肅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='986:1006'>拜爲䘮主則不手拜注云肅拜拜低頭也手拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1006:1026'>手至地也婦人以肅拜爲正㐫事乃手拜耳爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1026:1053'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-3a' );" name="016-3a" class="pb">[016-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1053:1073'>尸爲祖姑之尸也士虞禮曰男男尸女女尸爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1073:1093'>䘮主不拜手者爲夫與長子當稽顙也其餘亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1093:1113'>手拜而巳雖或爲唯或曰䘮爲主則不手拜肅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1113:1117'>拜也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1117:1129'>五虞祭婦人爲祖姑作尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1129:1149'>爲尸坐者謂虞祭婦人爲祖姑作尸也周禮坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1149:1169'>尸嫌婦人或異故明之也若平常祭無婦人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1169:1182'>尸示主於夫故設同几而巳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1182:1196'>　六昬禮婦拜扱地穆嬴頓首</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1196:1223'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-3b' );" name="016-3b" class="pb">[016-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1223:1243'>云婦人以肅拜爲正者言肅拜是婦人之常而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1243:1263'>昬禮婦拜扱地以其新來爲婦盡禮於舅姑故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1263:1283'>也左傳穆嬴頓首於宣子之門者有求於宣子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1283:1303'>非禮之正也云凶事乃手拜耳者言婦人除爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1303:1323'>䘮主其餘輕䘮凶事乃有手拜耳鄭知然者以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1323:1342'>經云爲䘮主則不手拜明不爲䘮主則手拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1342:1351'>七祭無跣燕有跣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1351:1371'>凡祭於室中堂上無跣燕則有之注云祭不跣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1371:1391'>者主敬也燕則有跣爲歡也天子諸侯祭有坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1391:1418'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-4a' );" name="016-4a" class="pb">[016-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1418:1438'>尸於堂之禮祭所尊在室燕所尊在堂將燕降</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1438:1445'>說屨乃升堂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1445:1454'>八貳車佐車倅車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1454:1474'>乗貳車則式佐車則否注云貳車佐車皆副車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1474:1494'>也朝祀之副曰貳戎獵之副曰佐魯莊公敗于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1494:1514'>乾時公䘮戎路傳乗而歸正義曰貳車云式主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1514:1534'>敬故謂朝祀之副曰貳佐車不式主武故云戎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1534:1554'>獵之副曰佐若戎獵相對則戎車之副曰倅田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1554:1574'>車之副曰佐故周禮戎僕馭倅車田僕馭佐車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1574:1601'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-4b' );" name="016-4b" class="pb">[016-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1601:1620'>熊氏曰此云戎獵之副曰佐者據諸侯禮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1620:1633'>　九有爵者乗馬服車不齒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1633:1653'>有貳車者之乗馬服車不齒注云尊有爵者之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1653:1673'>物廣敬也服車所乗車者車有新舊正義曰不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1673:1693'>敢齒次論其年歳評其價數髙下以尊者之物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1693:1696'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1696:1708'>十恭敬哀詡恭貌而敬心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1708:1728'>賔客主恭祭祀主敬䘮事主哀㑹同主詡注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1728:1748'>恭在貌也而敬又在心詡謂敏而有勇若齊國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1748:1775'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-5a' );" name="016-5a" class="pb">[016-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1775:1795'>佐正義曰成二年左傳齊晉戰於鞌齊國佐陳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1795:1808'>辭以拒晉師是敏而有勇也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1808:1825'><span class='krp-note'>十/一</span>冬時陽氣在魚腹夏在脊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1825:1845'>冬右腴者腴謂魚腹冬時陽氣下在魚腹故右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1845:1865'>腴夏右鰭者鰭謂魚脊夏時陽氣上在魚脊故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1865:1885'>右鰭凡陽所在之處肥美故進魚使嚮右以右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1885:1892'>手取之便也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1892:1909'><span class='krp-note'>十/二</span>車旁凡爲軓車旁九爲軌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1909:1929'>案周禮大馭祭兩軹祭軌此云祭左右軌范兩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1929:1956'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-5b' );" name="016-5b" class="pb">[016-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1956:1976'>文不同則左右軌與兩軹是一故云軓與軹於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1976:1996'>車同謂轊頭謂車轂小頭也此云范大馭云軌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1996:2016'>兩事是一聲同字異故云聲同謂式前之範與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2016:2037'>此范俱是式前也但式前之軓車旁著凡或作範</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2037:2057'>字聲同而字異即詩邶風濟盈不濡軓亦車旁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2057:2077'>凡與此同也若轂末之軌則車旁著九此經左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2077:2097'>右軌是也其車轍亦謂之軌亦車旁著九則考</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2097:2105'>工記經涂九軌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2105:2120'><span class='krp-note'>十/三</span>不食豢腴謂豬犬腸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2120:2147'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-6a' );" name="016-6a" class="pb">[016-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2147:2167'>君子不食圂腴注云周禮圂作豢謂犬豕之屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2167:2187'>食米榖者也腴有似於人穢正義曰腴豬犬腸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2187:2207'>也言豬犬亦食米榖其腹與人相似故君子但</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2207:2224'>食他處辟其腴謂腸胃也故鼎闕一也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2224:2241'><span class='krp-note'>十/四</span>設尊折爼行爵嘗羞之儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2241:2261'>尊者以酌者之左爲上尊尊壷者面其鼻飲酒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2261:2281'>者禨者醮者有折爼不坐未歩爵不嘗羞注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2281:2301'>尊者設尊者也酌者郷尊其左則右尊也鼻在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2301:2321'>面中言郷人也折爼尊徹之乃坐也巳沐飲曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2321:2348'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-6b' );" name="016-6b" class="pb">[016-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2348:2368'>機酌始冠曰醮歩行也正義曰庾云燕禮司宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2368:2388'>尊于東楹之西兩方壷左玄酒南上注玉藻云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2388:2408'>唯君面尊玄酒在南順君之面也下云公席阼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2408:2428'>階上西郷下又云執幂者升自西階立于尊南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2428:2448'>北面東上案左玄酒南上之言是設尊者東郷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2448:2468'>酌者西郷設者之右則酌者之左也又曰此謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2468:2488'>無筭爵之時若正羞脯醢折爼未飲則嘗之見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2488:2492'>郷飲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2492:2505'><span class='krp-note'>十/五</span>食飲勿氣辟咡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2505:2532'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-7a' );" name="016-7a" class="pb">[016-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2532:2552'>洗盥執食飲者勿氣有問焉則辟咡而對注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2552:2564'>示不敢歆臭也口旁曰咡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2564:2581'><span class='krp-note'>十/六</span>國家靡敝减損車服器馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2581:2601'>國家靡敝則車不雕幾甲不組縢食器不刻鏤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2601:2621'>君子不履絲屨馬不常秣注云靡敝賦稅亟也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2621:2641'>雕畫也幾附纒爲沂鄂也組縢以組飾之及紟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2641:2659'>帶也詩云公徒三萬貝胄朱綅亦鎧飾也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2659:2676'><span class='krp-note'>十/七</span>注䟽以刀禾枕皆有頴義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2676:2696'>云頴警枕也者以經枕外別言頴是頴發之義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2696:2723'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-7b' );" name="016-7b" class="pb">[016-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2723:2743'>故爲警枕刀卻刃授頴言授人以刀卻仰其刃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2743:2763'>授之以頴頴謂刀鐶也言以刀鐶授之頴是頴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2763:2783'>發之氣刀之在手謂之爲頴禾之秀穗亦謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2783:2803'>爲頴枕之警動亦謂之頴其事雖異大意同也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2803:2824'><span class='krp-note'>十/八</span>燕食所進魚體與祭祀饗食正禮異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2824:2844'>此濡魚進尾乾魚進首及右腴右鰭之屬皆謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2844:2864'>㝷常燕食所進魚體非祭祀及饗食正禮也若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2864:2884'>祭祀魚在於爼皆縮載爼旣橫設魚則隨爼而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2884:2904'>從於人爲橫無進首進尾之理故少牢魚用鮒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2904:2931'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-8a' );" name="016-8a" class="pb">[016-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2931:2951'>而爼縮載其主人正饗亦然公食大夫禮魚七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2951:2971'>縮爼是也正祭魚旣縮載少牢主人獻祝佐食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2971:2991'>三魚一橫之彼是正祭魚橫者以魚與牲體共</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2991:3011'>爼故特橫之殊於牲體也若天子諸侯繹祭及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3011:3031'>卿大夫儐尸魚則橫載之於爼爼在人前而橫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3031:3051'>魚則於人爲從得有進首尾也故有司徹云尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3051:3071'>爼五魚橫載之侑主人皆一魚亦横載之彼注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3071:3091'>云橫載之有異於牲體如鄭此言正祭之時牲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3091:3111'>體橫而魚縮載儐尸之時牲體縮而魚横載之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3111:3138'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-8b' );" name="016-8b" class="pb">[016-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3138:3158'>故云橫載之者異於牲體也正祭則右首進腴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3158:3178'>故少牢魚右首進腴變於主人若生人右首進</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3178:3198'>鰭故公食大夫云寢右注云右首也寢右進鰭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3198:3218'>也乾魚近腴多骨鯁案特牲少牢魚皆十有五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3218:3238'>鄭云從隂類昬禮魚有十四減一從偶數士䘮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3238:3258'>禮大斂及士虞禮及公食禮魚皆七其天子諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3258:3278'>侯魚數禾聞祭膴者膴謂刳魚腹下爲大臠此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3278:3293'>處肥美故食魚則刳取以祭先也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3293:3315'><span class='krp-note'>卄/一</span>未有燭告後至者執燭不讓不辤不歌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3315:3342'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-9a' );" name="016-9a" class="pb">[016-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3342:3362'>其未有燭而有後至者則以在者告道瞽亦然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3362:3382'>注爲其不見意欲知之也師冕見及階子曰階</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3382:3402'>也及席子曰席也皆坐子告之曰某在斯某在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3402:3422'>斯凡飲酒爲獻主者執燭抱燋客作而辭然後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3422:3442'>以授人爲宵言也主人親執燭敬賔示不倦也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3442:3462'>言獻主者容君使宰夫也未爇曰燋執燭不讓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3462:3482'>不辭不歌以燭繼晝禮殺正義曰凡飲酒爲獻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3482:3502'>主者獻主主人也謂爲飲酒主人法也凡飲酒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3502:3522'>主人自獻賔若尊卑不敵則使宰夫爲主人以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3522:3549'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '016-9b' );" name="016-9b" class="pb">[016-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3549:3569'>獻賔故云爲獻主也執燭者謂夜闇執燭抱燋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3569:3589'>者燋謂未爇之炬旣欲留客又取未然之炬抱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3589:3609'>之也客作而辭主人見客起辤故從辤而止以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3609:3629'>燭乃授己執事之人執燭不讓不辭不歌者執</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3629:3649'>燭夜時也禮賔主有讓及更相辭謝又各歌詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3649:3664'>相顯德今旣夜莫所以殺於三事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3664:3674'>禮記要義卷第十七</span><br/>
